 1920   '
 1930   *RaiseZPZ
 1940   local I%,W#
 1950   W#=Z#+poly(0,1)
 1960   Z#=poly(coeff(W#,0))
 1970   for I%=1 to deg(W#):Z#+=Z#(I%)*coeff(W#,I%):next
 1980   Z#=(Z#-poly(0,1))@U#
 1990   return
